# load colors and themes
load("~/Sync/R/R_themes/190123_theme_additions.Rda")
load("~/Sync/R/R_colors/190411_color_palettes.Rda")

# read 3C data
df <- read_excel("../Rex 3C data OCAB-KD.xlsx",range = "H1:R15")
## New names:
## * `` -> ...2
## * `` -> ...3
## * `` -> ...5
## * `` -> ...6
## * `` -> ...7
## *  and 3 more problems
colnames(df)
##  [1] "3C probe" "...2"     "...3"     "Scramble" "...5"     "...6"    
##  [7] "...7"     "OCA-B KD" "...9"     "...10"    "...11"
colnames(df) <- c("primer.name","probe.name","probe.coord",
                  "rep1.ctrl","rep2.ctrl","rep3.ctrl","rep4.ctrl",
                  "rep1.ocab","rep2.ocab","rep3.ocab","rep4.ocab")

# transform to long format / gather
dfg <- df %>% gather(-primer.name,-probe.name,-probe.coord,key = "sample",value = "frequency")

# add anchor and midpoint coordinates:
dfg$anchor.coord=187745300
dfg$mid.coord=(dfg$probe.coord+dfg$anchor.coord)/2

# recode sample to target and shRNA:
dfg$target <- gsub(".*\\.","",dfg$sample)
dfg$shRNA <- dfg %>% pull(target) %>% recode(ctrl="shCTRL",ocab="shOCAB")

Simple barplots

Bars realtive to location of bait/probe

# barplot
ggplot(dfg,aes(x=probe.coord,y=frequency,fill=shRNA))+geom_bar(stat = "summary", fun.y = "mean",position=position_dodge())+
  theme_linedraw()+theme_pub+labs(y="Relative\nFrequency",color="",x="")+guides(color=F)+
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("grey60","#336633"))+
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(187870000,188105000),expand = F) #chr3:187870000-188105000

ggsave("plot_barplot_3C_OCAB-KD.pdf",height = 1.5,width = 7.5)

Plots with arches

for the following plots, the main data shown will be the mean of all replicates

# summarize data 
dfs <- dfg %>% group_by(shRNA,probe.coord,anchor.coord,mid.coord,probe.name) %>% summarise(mean.frequency=mean(frequency))

# transform to long format / gather so as to plot anchor, midpoint and probe coordinates in one go
dfsg <- dfs %>% gather(-shRNA,-mean.frequency,-probe.name,key = point,value = coord)
# rename columns
dfsg$point <- gsub(".coord","",dfsg$point)
# add group column (for lines and smooth)
dfsg$group <- paste0(dfsg$shRNA,dfsg$probe.name)
# add thickness column to represent frequency with thickness of lines
dfsg$thickness <- dfsg$mean.frequency
# set anchor and probe frequency to 0:
dfsg$mean.frequency[dfsg$point %in% c("anchor","probe")] <- 0

Arches plot using all data

ggplot(dfsg,
       aes(x=coord,y=mean.frequency,color=shRNA,group=group))+
  geom_line(stat="smooth",alpha=0.8,method = "lm",formula = y ~ poly(x, 2), se = FALSE,lineend="round")+
  #geom_point(size=1,color="black")+
  theme_linedraw()+theme_pub+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("grey60","#336633"))+
  labs(y="Relative interaction\nfrequency",x="",color="")+guides(size=F)+
  theme(legend.justification = c(1, 1),legend.position = c(1, 1))

Arches plot for key probes
UCSC input region: chr3:187,730,000-187,995,000

ggplot(dfsg %>% filter(probe.name %in% c("B","G","J")),
       aes(x=coord,y=mean.frequency,color=shRNA,group=group))+
  geom_line(stat="smooth",method = "lm",formula = y ~ poly(x, 2), se = FALSE,lineend="round",
            size=2,alpha=0.8,)+
  theme_linedraw()+theme_pub+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("grey60","#336633"))+
  labs(y="Relative interaction\nfrequency",x="",color="")+guides(size=F)+
  theme(legend.justification = c(1, 1),legend.position = c(1, 1))+
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(187730000,187995000),expand = F)

ggsave("plot_3C_arches.pdf",height = 3,width = 7.5)

Arches plot with errorbars (non summarized data)

ggplot(dfsg %>% filter(probe.name %in% c("B","G","J")),
       aes(x=coord,y=mean.frequency,color=shRNA,group=group))+
  geom_line(stat="smooth",method = "lm",formula = y ~ poly(x, 2), se = FALSE,
            lineend="round",alpha=0.8,size=2)+
  geom_point(size=1,color="black")+
  stat_summary(data= dfg %>% filter(probe.name %in% c("B","G","J")),
               aes(x=mid.coord,y=frequency,group=shRNA),inherit.aes=F,
               fun.data = mean_se, geom = "errorbar",width=5000)+
  theme_linedraw()+theme_pub+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("grey60","#336633"))+
  labs(y="Relative interaction\nfrequency",x="",color="")+guides(size=F)+
  theme(legend.justification = c(1, 1),legend.position = c(1, 1))+
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(187730000,187995000),expand = F)

ggsave("plot_3C_arches_errorbars.pdf",height = 3,width = 7.5)

Arches plot with thickness for frequency

ggplot(dfsg %>% filter(probe.name %in% c("B","G","J")),
       aes(x=coord,y=mean.frequency,color=shRNA,size=thickness,group=group))+
  geom_line(stat="smooth",method = "lm",formula = y ~ poly(x, 2), se = FALSE,
            lineend="round",alpha=0.8)+
  theme_linedraw()+theme_pub+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("grey60","#336633"))+
  labs(y="Relative interaction\nfrequency",x="",color="")+guides(size=F)+
  theme(legend.justification = c(1, 1),legend.position = c(1, 1))+
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(187730000,187995000),expand = F)

ggsave("plot_3C_arches_thickness.pdf",height = 3,width = 7.5)
